text: Sandra Wagner-Sachse is a German archer. She was born on 9 September 1969. Wagner competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and at the 2000 Summer Olympics.Sandra Wagner-SachseSandra WAGNER == References == Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:German archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Germany Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Germany
